&lt;li&gt;Must have &lt;strong&gt;5&lt;/strong&gt; years of experience with (&lt;strong&gt;1&lt;/strong&gt;) back-end development using C# and (&lt;strong&gt;2&lt;/strong&gt;) scripting and automation using tools such as PowerShell or Azure CLI .&lt;/li&gt;
